name: Princess Time Toys
tag_list: princess-costumes, princess-dress-ups, costumes, kids, children, tutu, tutus, toys, disney
overview:
Princess Time Toys carries the finest toys, dress-ups, costumes and more for your prince or princess. Wonderful dress-up costumes that will enrich your children’s fantasy play and spark the imagination.

Whether celebrating Halloween or starring in their own version of a beloved fairy tale such as Cinderella, we have what you need. We offer a Deluxe Gowns for ages 1-10, teens and tweens, and sizes for mom (standard and plus size adult women’s costume) as well so she can attend that next fancy dress party too! Amongst our most popular costumes are the Belle, Sleeping Beauty, and Tinkerbell as well as other dancewear including tutus, boas and more. We offer the finest creations in princess attire and accessories that you’ll find anywhere including fun wigs that finish any costume. We carry only the best from Little Adventures, Disney, Creative Education of Canada, Disguise, Rubies, and Mud Pie

We also carry clothing for 18 inch Dolls like American Girl. Costumes, period dresses, sportswear, scout uniforms, and so much more. Add to that bedding, accessories, wooden doll furniture including bunk beds and an heirloom quality wooden doll armoire, and you’ll see we carry a full line of doll products.
